content:
There have been multiple '''battles that took place on [[Alaris Prime/Legends|Alaris Prime]]''' throughout galactic history:

*'''[[Skirmish on Alaris Prime]]''', a short lived conflict during the [[New Sith Wars]].
*'''[[Alaris Prime colonial war]]''', between [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiees]] and the [[Trade Federation/Legends|Trade Federation]]
*'''[[Battle of Alaris Prime (Hunt for the Decimator)]]''', a battle in the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] against a [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Separatist]] effort to re-obtain stolen activation codes
*'''[[Battle on Alaris]]''', an effort in the Clone Wars to free multiple [[Loyalist/Legends|loyalist]] captives.

